{"tid":1383573,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"對於往後抗爭 和理非/半勇武 一些建議","createTime":"2019-07-29T17:13:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T10:04:56.000Z","uid":21108,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"91982d5eedf0b64a99b40dfa80b82398a722fa0f","tid":1383573,"uid":21108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:13:55.000Z","msg":"首先對於和理非 + 半勇武(敢企前線本人係尊重既)<br />\n<br />\n1. 關於有人掉野 <br />\n<br />\n不要說 : 咪撚掉啦<br />\n試著說 : 要幾個同時掉 掉完就閃<br />\n<br />\n打仗都係一排火鎗射出去,成組遠攻掉先有威脅<br />\n俾人射到仆街,仲打唔還手係咪撞襯個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 關於玩火  <br />\n<br />\n請不要阻止 , 民意已經升級 鑑於班狗已經開鎗恆常化 催淚放題變日常<br />\n連記者都俾捕 理由係協助暴動 燒個火又算D乜?<br />\n<br />\n如果你連火都唔敢用 就唔好企前線啦  淆底行返後少少  <span style=\"color: red;\">用火緊記由底燒起</span><br />\n<br />\n3. 如果閣下FULL GEAR但又唔敢進攻 唔緊要<br />\n勇武需要你在場精神支持 其他事你唔敢 唔好阻人做 唔好再用民意<br />\n<br />\n當班狗同速龍衝上黎 你可以預備手上工具 掉出去嚇停班狗保護手足撤退<br />\n只要你地中排願意 唔係出黎打卡 到此一遊 幫到撒退已經救到好多手足<br />\n<br />\n4. 前線排位<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/07/30/TOYn16.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F07%2F30%2FTOYn16.jpeg&h=204a2669&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前線要維持防線但唔需要好密 有咩事後面有兩個身位轉身跑<br />\n鑑於728太多人踩人同<span style=\"color: red;\">前排掉裝備問題</span> 導致前線勇武走唔切俾捕<br />\n呢點真係要檢討  有人會問 另外多出黎既人手會去左邊  下個POST講 我地最大優勢係人數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">同埋唔該各位請帶走自己既GEAR!!!! 如果連俾狗逗你都驚 咁你出黎做乜撚野?<br />\n俾狗逗到D裝備又可以點 沒收左 唔係放人就要去臭格 <br />\n<br />\n728 有49個義士斷正去左臭格啦!!! 你發夢乜柒都無做去坐返48小時出黎有咩問題<br />\n你知唔知而家D裝備越黎越少啦 物資車係好撚危險 有D前線連飯都無得食呀!!!</span><br />\n<br />\n唔該人人自危 幫手保存資源!!!  你地可以做既盡做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/07/30/pGbTPC.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F07%2F30%2FpGbTPC.jpeg&h=85ee6a81&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b6a12953269e97de1614bfc003538995f3df75e","tid":1383573,"uid":245172,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:15:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8b21fbcc9a02f15509b131c29593dacd54cebb23","tid":1383573,"uid":121589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:16:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"30368be9702bffa1aee1540617732da61ef6f001","tid":1383573,"uid":7954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:16:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"47feddcfd664dcf166897ea50b6399b6f8021925","tid":1383573,"uid":121589,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:17:29.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"3c42727a4952efd444445d4929ef44c47819aa66","tid":1383573,"uid":121589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:19:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9b1ab304b2c97637eaca7fd894c8841ab1663951","tid":1383573,"uid":121589,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:22:05.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"49746db5fb9e7f489f725eab95b5b34566f65436","tid":1383573,"uid":121589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:23:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9efab6c63c6e355202230b2eaac790b2194a52f9","tid":1383573,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:24:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d341af66d1f678877977c608e2ec2f9cd1b152b","tid":1383573,"uid":2174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:25:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CPcabbi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCPcabbi.png&h=bac46862&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2326b64e43f93e34f647662849a1a8ee620a6bd6","tid":1383573,"uid":245172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9efab6c63c6e355202230b2eaac790b2194a52f9","tid":1383573,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:24:16.000Z","msg":"<img